{"tid":1789646,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"秦國中生被譏同性戀　「怒掏爸槍」混進4000人學校射殺同學","createTime":"2019-12-19T12:20:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T12:37:16.000Z","uid":32511,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"aa509083a11a11a6a15e39e8b5e0c2d9cad35d44","tid":1789646,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T12:20:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/szPA569JwWU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FszPA569JwWU&d=d86Hk5Pgd4X%2FjIl3nTqvfLBzIjlmttHRdZ2xAWa028c%3D&h=c19cc44e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/szPA569JwWU</a><br />\n<br />\n泰國一名未滿14歲的國中少年，因不滿長期受到同學言語欺凌，被嘲笑是同性戀，最後受不了，偷了父親的手槍到學校，朝該名同學的上身開槍。霸凌者當場破胸慘死，少年要逃跑時則被其他師生攔下。<br />\n <br />\n根據「AMARIN 34HD」報導，少年因為長期在校被貼上同性戀標籤，還受到各種身心霸凌，使他內心漸漸被怒火佔據。18日，因為終於無法忍受，帶著從父親那偷來的槍到學校，一路上躲過其他近4000名師生的耳目，趁霸凌者正在獨自換穿鞋子的時候，從背後朝霸凌者開槍。<br />\n <br />\n霸凌者胸口被射穿，最後慘死於血泊之中；少年行兇後，到廁所脫下便服和手套，再換上校服要偷溜出校園，但一到校門口就被保全和趕來的師生團團圍住。他坦承因為無法再吞忍這樣的侮辱，才會痛下殺手。<br />\n <br />\n死者母親莫拉克（Duangchan Kaew Morakot）表示，兒子平時是個好孩子，用心學習之外，也沒有取笑過行兇的少年；班主任則表示行兇少年的犯案動機還需要釐清，因為問少年為什麼要開槍打死朋友後，對方的回應像在玩遊戲。"},{"pid":"4dca0060daea4843f114b53b1716512343ce521c","tid":1789646,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T12:21:15.000Z","msg":"好驚9仔9女偷黑9槍返學校<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21372dcbb98c768eb58114fbbcaed37ddabf73f1","tid":1789646,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T12:21:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a2a6d73a5c8d59a713279fd1dacdcd547318277c","tid":1789646,"uid":326427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T12:22:21.000Z","msg":"［同我推上熱門］［行動］平安夜要經濟攬炒呀！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1786709\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1786709</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0aMiJK3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0aMiJK3.jpg&h=7645b339&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2507cee87f6955227097c77bcef01d01719e3662","tid":1789646,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T12:23:13.000Z","msg":"以為單人匹馬殺咗四千人咁勁"},{"pid":"ef5e1c764245dab94cbbb034753aa6ad5b57eb68","tid":1789646,"uid":243175,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T12:23:30.000Z","msg":"抵撚死啦笑9人"},{"pid":"d7ebc0cb02c9e82ead6aec524c8d4309ad7bcfd9","tid":1789646,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T12:24:33.000Z","msg":"連登仔應該已被處決左好耐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6380391c36ee3410cc47965ded6035b57b1d69f","tid":1789646,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T12:35:03.000Z","msg":"早幾日個單中學雞笑9義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8e8662cccced291624c30d89f515816f2c69849","tid":1789646,"uid":2364,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T12:37:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n死者母親莫拉克（Duangchan Kaew Morakot）表示，兒子平時是個好孩子，用心學習之外，<span style=\"color: red;\">也沒有取笑過行兇的少年</span>；班主任則表示行兇少年的犯案動機還需要釐清，因為問少年為什麼要開槍打死朋友後，對方的回應像在玩遊戲。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我個仔咁乖一定唔會恰人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}